  "body": "### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to see and copy full transaction hash (both for the current transaction and for past transactions) so that I can use it in other apps.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe the feature you would like, or briefly summarise the bug and what you did, what you expected to happen, and what actually happens. Sections below)\r\n*Summary*: Currently, in Main Wallet it's possible to see Transactions list with \r\n- not full address of recipient/sender with ... at the end (depends if it's in or out transaction )\r\n- Date and time of transaction\r\n- Sum that was transferred\r\n- \"+\" or \"-\" to show in and out transaction\r\n\r\nWhat users would like to have:\r\n1. For sure: possibility to see and copy transaction hash (not shown in current version)\r\n2. Most likely: possibility to see and copy an address of recipient/sender (not fully shown in current version)\r\n\r\nExamples of available fields/data on ROPSTEN TESTNET:\r\n* Transactions overview for address: https://testnet.etherscan.io/address/0xd0844aff4f66176702dd2ffd07dcc3731c5caab4\r\n* Details of a transaction: https://testnet.etherscan.io/tx/0x8e6848da62006a68259f97a78600c06ea613eae81429320c307cbf28447e805f\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what you expected to happen.)\r\nFor current transaction and for previous transactions: \r\n1. Transaction hash is visible to user and can be copied\r\n2. Sender/Receiver address is fully visible and can be copied \r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what actually happened.)\r\n1. Transaction hash can be found\r\n2. Address of receiver/sender is not fully visible and can't be copied\r\n![wallet ransactions](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/6584810/24450295/af4dde3e-147a-11e7-99b9-0d7401023216.jpg)\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n- Open Status and login\r\n- Send some contacts (both in contact list and with scan QR) some ETH\r\n- Receive some ETH from your contacts or via Scan QR\r\n- Open Wallet and check Transactions \r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n[comment]: # (Please summarise the solution and provide a task list on what needs to be fixed.)\r\n*Summary*: \r\n\r\n- [ ] Need new designs and interaction flows to include data on Transaction hash and full address of receiver/sender for past transactions and for current transaction\r\n- [ ] Implement designs\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\r\n* Status version: 0.9.4\r\n* Operating System: Android and iOS\r\n\r\nInstabug:\r\n* https://dashboard.instabug.com/applications/status/beta/bugs/171\r\n* https://dashboard.instabug.com/applications/status-10bb8cbc-15f6-44f0-8c7a-db478dc34d7d/beta/bugs/321\r\n",
